OL,3,CWatchdog concludes probe into fatal
OL,4,Caccident at Stratford Underground
OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FThe Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,8,F(RAIB) has published its findings on
OL,9,Fan incident at Stratford London
OL,10,FUnderground station, where a passenger
OL,11,Fdied after falling onto the tracks on
OL,12,FBoxing Day 2023.
OL,14,F72-year-old Brian Mitchell had been
OL,15,Fvisiting friends and had traveled
OL,16,Fusing TfL buses earlier that day
OL,17,Fbefore entering the underground
OL,18,Fnetwork at Stanmore station, the
OL,19,Freport stated.
