OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FFurther details reveal Mr Mitchell
OL,8,Falighted from the Jubilee train at
OL,9,FStratford Underground Station at
OL,10,Faround 13:57 and sat on a platform
OL,11,Fbench. At around 14:45 he stood up but
OL,12,Fimmediately stumbled forwards and fell
OL,13,Ffrom the platform onto the track.
OL,15,FThe report said Mr Mitchell fell at a
OL,16,Ftime when there were no other
OL,17,Fpassengers or staff present on the
OL,18,Fplatform, and there was no
OL,19,Fintervention made to prevent the first
OL,20,Ftrain from arriving.
