OL,3,CWatchdog concludes probe into fatal
OL,4,Caccident at Stratford Underground
OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FRAIB found that the operator of the
OL,8,Ffirst train did not see the passenger
OL,9,Fon the track ahead of the train as it
OL,10,Farrived at the platform. It concluded
OL,11,Fthat this was possibly because their
OL,12,Flevel of attention was reduced due to
OL,13,Fthe use of automatic train operation.
OL,15,FMr Mitchell lay undiscovered on the
OL,16,Ftrack for five minutes before being
OL,17,Fstruck by an incoming train, the
OL,18,Fwatchdog said. A further three inbound
OL,19,Ftrains entered the platform over a
OL,20,Fperiod of time with him remaining on
OL,21,Fthe track.
