OL,7,FThe RIAB found the severity of the
OL,8,Faccident was compounded by a series of
OL,9,Fmissed opportunities to intervene. The
OL,10,Foperator of the second inbound train
OL,11,Fdid not notice the passenger, while
OL,12,Fthe third train's operator saw
OL,13,Fsomething on the track but failed to
OL,14,Fidentify it as a person.
