OL,7,FDespite being aware of the situation,
OL,8,Fa customer service assistant on the
OL,9,Fplatform did not stop the fourth train
OL,10,Fas it entered the station. Although
OL,11,Fthe fourth train's operator recognised
OL,12,Fa person on the track, they did not
OL,13,Fbring their train to a halt.
