OL,3,CWatchdog concludes probe into fatal
OL,4,Caccident at Stratford Underground
OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FThe RAIB identified issues linked to
OL,8,Fautomatic train operation (ATO),
OL,9,Ffinding that its repetitive nature can
OL,10,Flead to 'underload,' 'reducing
OL,11,Foperators' attentiveness and
OL,12,Fincreasing the risk of distraction. At
OL,13,Fterminus stations, some operators were
OL,14,Ffound to prepare for leaving their
OL,15,Ftrains before they had fully stopped,
OL,16,Fdiverting focus from critical
OL,17,Foperational tasks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
