OL,4,Caccident at Stratford Underground
OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FWhile London Underground Limited had
OL,8,Fassessed the risks of platform falls,
OL,9,Fthe RAIB concluded that existing
OL,10,Fsafety measures at Stratford station
OL,11,Fwere insufficient to prevent this
OL,12,Ftragic accident.
OL,14,FLilli Matson, TfL's Chief Safety
OL,15,FOfficer said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,16,Fwith the family and friends of Mr.
OL,17,FMitchell, who sadly died at Stratford
OL,18,FTube station on 26 December 2023.
