OL,7,F"We welcome the recommendations from
OL,8,Fthe RAIB's independent investigation
OL,9,Finto this incident, which align with
OL,10,Fthe findings of our own internal
OL,11,Finvestigation, and work has already
OL,12,Fbegun to implement them.
OL,14,F"We will always strive to learn from
OL,15,Fincidents and improve operational
OL,16,Fsafety, including by ensuring relevant
OL,17,Fregulatory bodies are immediately
OL,18,Finformed, carrying out thorough and
OL,19,Fextensive internal investigations and
OL,20,Fprioritising taking action on any
OL,21,Frecommendations from any review.
